Revision history for Mojolicious::Plugin::ValidateTiny

0.01
        First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

0.02
        Added "skip" config option

0.03
        Better docs

0.04
        Added "on_errror" option
        Recreating HTML::Lint object on each request because it does not reset own state

0.05
        Upgrade to HTML::Lint 2.26
        Disable smartmatch warning
        Split tests into subtests

0.06
        Fi experimental smartmatch warning
